00:02:06.460 --> 00:02:08.960
And then "Science Analysts
Frontier" is a sort of outcome

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:11.310
of the end of the war,
looking forward.

00:02:11.310 --> 00:02:14.730
And all of those things I think
have a big impact on the

00:02:14.730 --> 00:02:20.520
MIT that you experience today
and the landscape of how

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:23.300
science is funded and organized
in this country that

00:02:23.300 --> 00:02:26.890
you'll experience, probably
regardless of whether you go

00:02:26.890 --> 00:02:30.010
into a research career or a
career in industry, certainly

00:02:30.010 --> 00:02:33.520
if you go into a career
in research, how

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:34.770
technology gets generated.

