with jet propulsion.

00:27:39.070 --> 00:27:41.882
But they were founded, under the
direction of Theodore von

00:27:41.882 --> 00:27:45.550
Karman, to do rocket
research basically.

00:27:45.550 --> 00:27:48.010
There's a whole new institution
out there created

00:27:48.010 --> 00:27:51.310
right about the same time,
by the same thing.

00:27:51.310 --> 00:27:53.780
The Applied Physics Lab
at Johns Hopkins.

00:27:53.780 --> 00:27:55.810
Anybody ever hear of that lab?

00:27:55.810 --> 00:27:58.050
Also a big government lab,
associated with the

00:27:58.050 --> 00:27:59.790
university.

00:27:59.790 --> 00:28:02.560
They do all kinds of interesting
secret stuff.

00:28:02.560 --> 00:28:05.915
They do submarine tracking and
they do a lot of space design

00:28:05.915 --> 00:28:07.220
and they build satellites.

00:28:07.220 --> 00:28:10.925
And in fact, the former
head of NASA, Mike

00:28:10.925 --> 00:28:13.710
Griffin came out of there.

00:28:13.710 --> 00:28:17.090
And they were founded in the
same period to develop the

00:28:17.090 --> 00:28:19.530
