a little radar device.

00:28:19.530 --> 00:28:21.770
It was built into an
artillery shell.

00:28:21.770 --> 00:28:24.280
It was designed to explode when
it came near an airplane.

00:28:26.820 --> 00:28:30.980
So these are all places
that still exist.

00:28:30.980 --> 00:28:34.320
A lot of these big government
or quasi-government research

00:28:34.320 --> 00:28:35.570
labs exist.

