guy, an anti-aircraft gunner,

00:29:47.080 --> 00:29:48.330
aboard a Naval ship.

00:29:48.330 --> 00:29:51.960
And what it does is it's got
two gyroscopes in it.

00:29:51.960 --> 00:29:55.510
And it has a little mirror and
it automatically calculates

00:29:55.510 --> 00:29:57.230
the lead for the gunner.

00:29:57.230 --> 00:30:00.880
So if there's an airplane coming
in and you've got to

00:30:00.880 --> 00:30:05.260
lead it by some amount in order
to fire ahead of it,

00:30:05.260 --> 00:30:08.150
because it takes time for the
bullets to get there, and it

00:30:08.150 --> 00:30:10.520
can be very hard to train people
to do that, that's how

00:30:10.520 --> 00:30:12.640
