the work that gets done at MIT

00:31:09.240 --> 00:31:12.450
is not just the microwave
physics itself, but the user

00:31:12.450 --> 00:31:14.130
interfaces for a lot
of these things.

00:31:14.130 --> 00:31:16.690
And building on that work that
we talked about with the

00:31:16.690 --> 00:31:20.110
differential analyzer, how you
actually kind of match these

00:31:20.110 --> 00:31:23.300
systems to human performance
is really one of the big

00:31:23.300 --> 00:31:24.360
themes in the research.

00:31:24.360 --> 00:31:27.400
And that sort of leads us
obviously up through Weiner

00:31:27.400 --> 00:31:28.650
and cybernetics.

00:31:30.730 --> 00:31:35.370
This is one of the divisions of
the NDRC, which was devoted

00:31:35.370 --> 00:31:39.320
