00:32:44.430 --> 00:32:48.590
He invented the word "digital"
and built all kinds of control

00:32:48.590 --> 00:32:51.840
computers out of telephone
relays during the war.

00:32:51.840 --> 00:32:52.800
This guy is Ivan Getting.

00:32:52.800 --> 00:32:54.450
And I'll talk about him
in a little bit.

00:32:54.450 --> 00:32:56.610
He did a lot of the early
work on radar.

00:32:56.610 --> 00:32:59.480
And later on, was really
the father of the GPS

00:32:59.480 --> 00:33:04.180
constellation, that we now
use to navigate our cars.

00:33:04.180 --> 00:33:06.150
Karl Wildes, also a electrical
engineering

00:33:06.150 --> 00:33:08.740
professor here at MIT.

00:33:08.740 --> 00:33:11.950
George Philbrick, who really
kind of invented the analog

00:33:11.950 --> 00:33:14.140
computer, electrical
analog computer.

00:33:14.140 --> 00:33:17.290
