00:34:18.595 --> 00:34:23.380
The first op amps are invented
to go into this device.

00:34:23.380 --> 00:34:25.969
And the whole idea of a feedback
amplifier being used

00:34:25.969 --> 00:34:29.560
to do addition and subtraction
and multiplication and

00:34:29.560 --> 00:34:32.620
division and integration and
differentiation, all comes out

00:34:32.620 --> 00:34:36.194
of this device, from again, from
the telephone company.

