about anti-aircraft fire

00:34:58.620 --> 00:35:01.136
control during the
Second World War.

00:35:01.136 --> 00:35:05.110
And of course, now we have the
idea of cyberspace and cyber

00:35:05.110 --> 00:35:08.800
this, and my Sony Cyber-shot,
and all this kind of stuff.

00:35:08.800 --> 00:35:13.680
The basic ideas of a lot of
this came from people like

00:35:13.680 --> 00:35:16.700
